General.Name: 360 Finance Inc
General.Description: Qifu Technology, Inc., together with its subsidiaries, operate AI-empowered credit-tech platform under the Qifu Jietiao brand in the People's Republic of China. The company provides credit-driven services that match borrowers with financial institutions to conduct borrower acquisition, credit assessment, fund matching, and post-facilitation services; and platform services, including loan facilitation and post-facilitation services to financial institution partners under an intelligence credit engine, referral services, and other technology solutions. It serves financial institutions, consumers, and small and micro-enterprises. The company was formerly known as 360 DigiTech, Inc. and changed its name to Qifu Technology, Inc. in March 2023. Qifu Technology, Inc. was founded in 2016 and is headquartered in Shanghai, the People's Republic of China.
